<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-57-1054 </DOCNO><TEXT>At the National Institute for Chemical Engineering Research (NICER), CSIR,a considerable effort is being devoted to research and development ofcatalysts and catalytic processes for use in the South African syntheticfuels industry. Work is being done in close co-operation with variousindustries and other bodies having a direct interest in the local productionof liquid transportation fuels from coal and natural gas. Research onimprovements to Fischer-Tropsch catalysts and alternatives to the Fischer-Tropschsynthesis is described.</TEXT></DOC>